lead_paragraph: Cody Anderson allowed only three hits in 6 2/3 innings, four Cleveland teammates homered and the Indians beat the Texas Rangers 9-1 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Anderson Sharp for Indians in 9-1 Win Over Rangers
